&lt;p&gt;Chef Takashi Saito is a young but very accomplished chef with accolades such as &lt;strong&gt;#43&lt;/strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Asia&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Restaurants&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;3&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;Michelin Stars&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;#92 on Elite Traveller 2014 World&rsquo;s Top 100 List &lt;/strong&gt;to his credit.&nbsp; The small restaurant allows for personal attention and the ability for guests to watch Chef Saito in action, demonstrating his meticulous attention to detail. Business casual attire; Jackets preferred for gentlemen. &nbsp; Please contact Sushi Saito by phone at +81 03-3589-4412 to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time and either a cell phone number or a local number in Tokyo where the restaurant can reach you if necessary. Also provide any details if this is a special occasion or if there are allergies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
